{"tid":942013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嘲對手英文差 美國小姐道歉","createTime":"2018-12-15T10:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T12:14:38.000Z","uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"89b68bb4f39c0c8341f37db740aea73f775560f2","tid":942013,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T10:05:23.000Z","msg":"嘲對手英文差 美國小姐道歉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20181215/s00060/cbfdb2adfb4e741da68fa165b1df59f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20181215%2Fs00060%2Fcbfdb2adfb4e741da68fa165b1df59f2.jpg&h=8283c7a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1之1<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】國際選美比賽環球小姐（Miss Universe）將於下周一（17日）在泰國曼谷舉行，美國代表、24歲的薩默斯（圖）周三（12日）被揭嘲笑柬埔寨和越南代表的英語能力差，她隨即於翌日就不當言論道歉。<br />\n<br />\n有關片段周三出現在哥倫比亞代表莫拉萊斯（Valeria Morales）的Instagram帳戶。在短片中，薩默斯（Sarah Rose Summers）稱越南代表倪函（H'Hen Nie，音譯）「裝作懂得大部分英語，但向她提問和對話後，她就只會點頭和微笑。真可愛」，其間她更模仿倪函的動作；薩默斯又指柬埔寨的西納特（Rern Sinat）不會說英語，亦沒有人懂她的語言。<br />\n<br />\n片段曝光後，不少網民批評薩默斯是仇外和自以為高高在上。薩默斯周四在Instagram貼文稱，那些說話的原意是讚賞部分姊妹的勇氣，但「現在發現這些言論會被視為不尊重」，她就此道歉。<br />\n<br />\n（今日美國報）"},{"pid":"9fccf42eba54a1a14373ba5021f4c22dd15a40b6","tid":942013,"uid":33077,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T10:41:57.000Z","msg":"幾靚都輸啦<br />\n睇低人"},{"pid":"38ff22363e64888fd031097ac2beb1bd9f6b8682","tid":942013,"uid":53026,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T10:48:33.000Z","msg":"點解咁後生就有表情紋"},{"pid":"2171121d9e33eb9827d33b685301adfacda2f037","tid":942013,"uid":132038,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T10:57:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15e70ca1c0093b74ea6477c24eea6f378378f36a","tid":942013,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T10:59:50.000Z","msg":"要拍打佢大屎忽"},{"pid":"c394ca1436d2209ac35738ad6c02370c9ebb45c9","tid":942013,"uid":143241,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T11:00:17.000Z","msg":"美國人除咗英文之外就唔識講其他語言,有咩資格笑人？"},{"pid":"5d74e29fb85ea060185440b64833e25e7e214660","tid":942013,"uid":32527,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T11:04:41.000Z","msg":"美國人係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇唔起其他人"},{"pid":"a6e088f81a184f4194b2833fb10a208acad300cf","tid":942013,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T11:07:47.000Z","msg":"試過有日女遊客唔識英文畀人開槍射尻死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5356ff394e74d6dca99372426157692ff77e8e59","tid":942013,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2171121d9e33eb9827d33b685301adfacda2f037","tid":942013,"uid":132038,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"quote":{"pid":"9fccf42eba54a1a14373ba5021f4c22dd15a40b6","tid":942013,"uid":33077,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T10:41:57.000Z","msg":"幾靚都輸啦<br />\n睇低人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T10:57:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T11:07:48.000Z","msg":"識講英文嘅白痴依舊係個白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de70a9b5c0c64e2a59504f5a7eae5e1a7cff4a4","tid":942013,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c394ca1436d2209ac35738ad6c02370c9ebb45c9","tid":942013,"uid":143241,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T11:00:17.000Z","msg":"美國人除咗英文之外就唔識講其他語言,有咩資格笑人？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T11:10:31.000Z","msg":"都唔係西南嗰d都識d西斑牙話<br />\n北部就識d法文"},{"pid":"251a99a7676b0e1eadcebc99e7f8c18dd1649acf","tid":942013,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9de70a9b5c0c64e2a59504f5a7eae5e1a7cff4a4","tid":942013,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c394ca1436d2209ac35738ad6c02370c9ebb45c9","tid":942013,"uid":143241,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T11:00:17.000Z","msg":"美國人除咗英文之外就唔識講其他語言,有咩資格笑人？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"